Package com.domain.service

Class SpecialsRequestsService

java.lang.Object
com.domain.service.SpecialsRequestsService
All Implemented Interfaces:
SpecialsRequestsApi
public class SpecialsRequestsService extends Object implements SpecialsRequestsApi
Class to perform SpecialsRequestsService business treatments. Implements SpecialsRequestsApi to send responses to controllers in the infrastructure layer.
See Also:

  • Use the FirestationSpi to get data from the infrastructure layer.

  • Use the MedicalrecordsSpi to get data from the infrastructure layer.
  • Use the PersonSpi to get data from the infrastructure layer.

  • Annotated with @DomainService to be considered a Bean by the infrastructure layer.
